title: Elvis Costello Takes The Colbert Questionert
description:
If you don't know his favorite sandwich, or the name of the most used app on his phone, do you really know Elvis Costello? Find out how Elvis fared under the intense scrutiny of The Colbert Questionert and check out his latest album, "The Boy Named If."
